> The other part might be described as a positive vacuum valve, although I don't
> know. It is disc shaped with one male connection on one side and two on the
> other. Two tubes attach to one side and another on the other side which leads
> into the fuel regulator. It's a Bosch. I called the Bus Depot to get the part
